Classified as Least Concern (as 
<taxonomicName id="078B4D5DED567D72BCB6FEA6C2FE71AE" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1920" box="[2295,2519,379,408]" class="Mammalia" family="Dipodidae" genus="Allactaga" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="11" pageNumber="92" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="hotsoni">Allactaga hotsoni</taxonomicName>
) and Data Deficient (as A. firouzi) on The IUCN Red Lust.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
